{
  "stem": "21786.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And there were bunks, triple bunks, and people were sleeping approximately six or eight abreast, with few blankets thrown over them, if that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Usually there was some kind of a straw mat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Sometimes there was no straw mat, just the wooden planks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Now, our block elders, meaning the oldest of the block, was training the guys how to respond when an SS man walks in, or when he calls simply to attention, how quickly they have to respond.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They have to respond within 30 seconds, under 30 seconds, holding a cane in his hand.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It went all night, training how to do this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He killed five people with a stick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was, I mean, an exercise with utmost brutality, which simply was so unexpected.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We suddenly-- I mean, I've seen something-- we were present to something which just was shattering.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at the same time, we were explained, don't make-- don't make big fuss about it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just take a big whiff.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What do you smell?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Do you think that they are roasting a pig, or they are roasting a chicken there?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They are roasting the Jews there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You are about 200 meters away from the gas chambers and from the crematoria.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's what you smell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's the smell of the burned bodies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I believed it immediately.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were people simply who couldn't believe that such a thing is possible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there, about four days later, I met with Eva in a washroom, a block where there were faucets, and where sometimes water was running and where we were permitted to wash.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Women, men.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Didn't make any difference.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We didn't realize how lucky we are that there are women and children, and everybody in the same camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
